snippet.title: Finally, the kinda affordable 7DoF robot arm (Amber B1)
snippet.description:
Finally, the affordable 7 axis (better than 6axis!) robotic arm is here! Amber Bionic 1 has really impressive performance. It has the payload of 3kg and the precision of less than 0.5mm. And all this with very affordable price!

The link to the KickStarter campaign: https://bit.ly/3tvuYTc

Special thanks to my special Patrons: Matthew Harrison, RobotDigg Shanghai, Shounak Bhattacharya and Vikas Marwaha!

Please subscribe. This will help me to develop other projects like this, to bring the bright future closer!
